"""
        Test that the inequality operator returns True when comparing two
        SymmetricKey objects with different data.
        """
a = SymmetricKey(enums.CryptographicAlgorithm.AES, 128, self.bytes_128a)
b = SymmetricKey(enums.CryptographicAlgorithm.AES, 256, self.bytes_256a)
self.assertTrue(a != b)
self.assertTrue(b != a)
